h2_title: Yaoguai Chief Miniboss Fight - Elder Amourworm
content: Exit back to where you saw the mysterious women, and look to the right to find a mural with a green Wisp in front of it, and a pathway leading left. Take the path, and you'll find it leads down below the bridge you crossed earlier and over to the group of houses the other path led to.
